comments: Thompson (GSW) brings his left forearm toward Gordon's (DEN) front and marginal contact occurs during the drive to the basket.
Thompson (GSW) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Gordon (DEN) prior to incidental arm contact occurring.
Wiggins (GSW) gives a step of distance when establishing himself in Jackson's (DEN) path and marginal contact occurs during the screen.
Looney (GSW) establishes himself in Porter Jr.'s (DEN) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) places his forearm against Curry (GSW) as the two players engage, but he does not dislodge him from his defensive position.
Thompson (GSW) places his right hand on Jackson's (DEN) body as he moves towards the basket, but the contact is marginal.
Gordon (DEN) pivots off of his foot and steps out of bounds while still in possession of the ball.
Wiggins (GSW) initiates illegal contact with Caldwell-Pope (DEN) that affects his SQBR as he receives the pass.
Wiggins (GSW) briefly places both hands on Jokic (DEN) on the perimeter, but the contact does not affect his FOM.
Paul (GSW) commits a take foul on Jokic (DEN).
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) maintains a legal guarding position during Curry's (GSW) drive to the basket.
Moody's (GSW) right foot is out of bounds when he jumps to attempt to save the loose ball.  Upon touching the ball, an out-of-bounds violation is correctly called.
Wiggins (GSW) extends both hands forward and initiates contact with Jackson (DEN), which affects Jackson's SQBR.
